high_descs: Move to the counter where the sink is.
Pick up the knife from the edge of the counter.
Turn right, move to the table where the stool is.
Cut the apple into sections.
Turn left, move to in front of the stove.
Place the knife into the pan on the right.
Turn left, move to the table where the stool is.
Pick up a section of apple.
Turn left, move to in front of the stove.
Place the apple section into the pan on the right.
Pick up the pan with the apple section in it.
Turn left, move to the refrigerator.
Place the pan on to a shelf of the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple into sections, place a section into the refrigerator.

high_descs: Look down towards the metal sink.
Pick up the knife with the silver handle.
Turn around and face the white table on the right.
Cut the yellow fruit into three pieces.
Turn left and face the white stove on your left.
Pace the knife in the pan on the back right stove top.
Turn left three times until you are facing the white table.
Pick up a slice of the golden yellow fruit nearest you.
Turn left and face the stove on your left again.
Place the slice in the pan on the back right stove top.
Pick up the pan that is on the back right stove top
Turn around and face the silver refrigerator.
Place the pan on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place slice of fruit on the top shelf in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Face the sink under the microwave with knives on it.
Pick the silver knife up off of the sink.
Turn around and go towards the white kitchen table.
Cut the apple on the table into 3 slices.
Go to the left and face the stove.
Place the knife in the pot on the rear right burner.
Turn around and face the kitchen table to the left again.
Pick up one slice of the apple.
Turn to left and walk towards and face the stove again.
Place the apple slice in the pan on the rear right burner.
Pick up the pan with the apple slice and knife in it.
Turn around and face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the pan inside, then shut the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan with the items in it inside of the refrigerator.

high_descs: look down at sink
take knife with silver handle
turn around and cross room to rectangular table with coffee maker
slice the apple on the table with the knife
turn left and go to in front of stove
put knife in pan on back right burner of stove
return to in front of sliced apple on rectangular table
take apple wedge from the table
return to stand in front of the stove
put apple in pan with knife
take the pan with the knife and the apple from the back right burner of the stove
turn around and cross the room to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator, place the pan on the grey plate, and close the refrigerator door
anns.task_desc: place a pan, containing a knife and an apple slice, in the refrigerator

high_descs: Back up just a little bit to see the sink in front of you.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter right in front of the sink.
Turn around and go to the table with the apple and coffee pot on it.
Use the butter knife to cut the apple.
Turn to the left and go to the stove.
Put the butter knife in the pot that is on the back left stove burner.
Turn around and go back to the table.
Pick up a piece of the apple.
Turn to the left and go back to the stove.
Put the apple in the same pot with the butter knife.
Pick up the pot with the apple and butter knife in it.
Turn left, go forward a little bit, turn left again and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the pot inside, close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot containing a butter knife and piece of apple into the fridge.
